{"tid":2173670,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"原告變被告 - 林夕","createTime":"2020-08-25T11:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T11:36:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"99d9c20e848e745732bb90acd79929490525f005","tid":2173670,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:19:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200825/4VJIUQQJQVA7JJKU467LMFQBK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200825%2F4VJIUQQJQVA7JJKU467LMFQBK4%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=2eb72dec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200825%2F4VJIUQQJQVA7JJKU467LMFQBK4%2F&h=e0729f41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200825/4VJIUQQJQVA7JJKU467LMFQBK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n原告變被告 - 林夕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BcMwbxCLntyGpHh_Q5XjliMBIjU=/1279x877/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BHHFAZNDF5H27OEEZYE4BIPAUY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBcMwbxCLntyGpHh_Q5XjliMBIjU%3D%2F1279x877%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBHHFAZNDF5H27OEEZYE4BIPAUY.png&h=7847161e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法院上的正義女神像會矇着眼睛，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當今香港的正義女神，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在一個人擠人的晚上，一個大意而小心的司機，開車衝上人行道，見人撞人；一個倒楣的議員，把這危險駕駛人士告上法庭。結果，撞傷人的不用上庭，提出私人刑事檢控的反而要收律師信，被追討訟費。<br />\n<br />\n路見不平的一個不小心要賠償八萬二千大元；不小心就撞傷三個人，其中一人斷掉雙腿的，擁有不上庭受審的自由，因為提出控訴的，不是別人，而是許智峯，一個失去維持公義自由的尊貴立法會議員。<br />\n<br />\n正義女神成為被操控的提線木偶，劍指不受政府歡迎人士，天不開眼，女神像卻睜開眼，看見許智峯是警方眼中釘，那天秤開始呃秤，替警方出一口氣的，可以秤先啲。<br />\n<br />\n原告變被告，鄭若驊專業果然是仲裁調解，沒事的，沒事的，撞傷人而已，一切好辦。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n矇眼正義女神像原型來自希臘。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"611dbaab81a914785850223e5cd054286be06a6c","tid":2173670,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}